    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained by its previous owners. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts reliably, making it an excellent choice for anyone seeking a dependable daily driver. While it shows some minor signs of normal wear, the interior is clean and all major systems are functioning as they should. You can expect a solid, road-ready car that provides a comfortable and safe driving experience.",
