    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a dedicated project car or a source for parts. The exterior shows significant wear, including heavy rust on the wheel arches, several large dents on the passenger side, and a failing clear coat. Mechanically, the engine currently runs roughly and will likely require a full overhaul, and the transmission is slipping in second gear. The interior has suffered from sun damage, with cracked upholstery and a non-functional dashboard display. It is being sold strictly as-is.",
