    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this dependable daily driver that\u2019s ready to hit the road! While it shows some honest signs of its journey so far, it remains a solid and reliable choice for anyone looking for great value. It\u2019s a practical, hardworking vehicle that\u2019s perfect for getting you where you need to go with confidence!",
